          <div class="point-card">
            <h4>Recruitment</h4>
            <p>Children were often forced into fighting, manipulated by commanders promising revenge or survival.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="point-card">
            <h4>Drugs & Violence</h4>
            <p>"Brown brown" (a cocaine and gunpowder mix) was used to desensitize and control young fighters.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="point-card">
            <h4>Loss of Innocence</h4>
